      "boundary_map_markdown": "### S01 → S02\n\nProduces:\n- `audioGraph.ts` — singleton module exporting: `initGraph()`, `setVolume(v)`, `getVolume()`, `playSource(url)`, `pause()`, `resume()`, `seek(t)`, `getCurrentTime()`, `getDuration()`, `getAnalyserNode()`, `getInsertionPoint()`, `onEnded(callback)`\n- `PlayerContext` refactored — useReducer actions delegate to audioGraph instead of globalAudio\n- Volume controlled via GainNode (0.0–1.0 range)\n\nConsumes:\n- nothing (first slice)\n\n### S01 → S03\n\nProduces:\n- Dual HTMLAudioElement architecture — two elements created at init, both connected via createMediaElementSource\n- `audioGraph.ts` exports: `preloadSource(url)`, `swapToPreloaded()`, `getActiveElement()`, `getInactiveElement()`\n- Source lifecycle management — which element is active, which is on standby\n\nConsumes:\n- nothing (first slice)\n\n### S02 → S03\n\nProduces:\n- localStorage read/write utilities for audio preferences\n- Initial state hydration pattern — PlayerContext reads from localStorage on mount\n\nConsumes from S01:\n- `audioGraph.getVolume()` / `audioGraph.setVolume(v)` for volume persistence\n- PlayerContext refactored state (shuffle, repeat accessible for persistence)"
